    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2010900/extras/92a07330ae93795ab7eb13876843daf5.avif?t=1771419265\" alt=\"游戏简介\" width=568 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款「虚构的，但也应当是合理的三国背景的」战棋类游戏，又似可将它看作是一段异位面的三国历史。我们不妨设想，主人公——「廖豪」本就存在于彼时的东汉，只是因为一点点选择上的不同，遂形成了这个与正史判然有别的故事，亦造就了一个「平行宇宙」。而这个游戏的剧情，就是以此人的视角来讲述一段本位面中并不存在的三国历史。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >因而诸君或将发现，游戏前期的剧情尚可称作较为熟知的三国故事，但是剧情愈后，和本位面差别愈大，许多在正史上着墨甚少乃至寥寥数笔的人物，亦可能在这段迥异的时空中绽放出别样的光芒。若诸君仍有兴趣一览这阙于史籍之轶闻，不妨一试。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2010900/extras/60ee9fac184b7530340cb78cc60b5a13.poster.avif?t=1771419265\" width=800 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2010900/extras/60ee9fac184b7530340cb78cc60b5a13.webm?t=1771419265\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2010900/extras/60ee9fac184b7530340cb78cc60b5a13.mp4?t=1771419265\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2010900/extras/542b3db609dde82bffddd0ec188d6927.avif?t=1771419265\" alt=\"内容特色\" width=568 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在目前版本的游戏中，您将会体验到：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >至少25小时的游戏时长，包含50个风格各异的关卡</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >逾45万字的剧情文本，二百余名后汉三国历史人物演出的汉末异闻 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >参考大量原始文献与学者著述而编写的剧本、事典与列传，体验「合乎逻辑」的虚构故事</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与《曹操传》《火焰之纹章》均有差异的独特策略系统，通过加点和转职系统自由培养您的部队</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >满足特定条件以开启四个小型分支关卡，体验不同的事件</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >数量繁多的武器、宝物和特有的军略系统</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >咸宜于不同玩家的难度设置，自剧情爱好者到战棋深度玩家皆可依自身需求体验游戏</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发掘各关卡中的隐藏要素，达成44个Steam成就</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2010900/extras/14117ef06ba02237ce8ee1f552e6b8a3.poster.avif?t=1771419265\" width=450 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2010900/extras/14117ef06ba02237ce8ee1f552e6b8a3.webm?t=1771419265\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2010900/extras/14117ef06ba02237ce8ee1f552e6b8a3.mp4?t=1771419265\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2010900/extras/c531b56ecce01a3722accb50eb016030.poster.avif?t=1771419265\" width=260 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2010900/extras/c531b56ecce01a3722accb50eb016030.webm?t=1771419265\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2010900/extras/c531b56ecce01a3722accb50eb016030.mp4?t=1771419265\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2010900/extras/c76acae89d43a17e3bdddb469a684552.poster.avif?t=1771419265\" width=460 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2010900/extras/c76acae89d43a17e3bdddb469a684552.webm?t=1771419265\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2010900/extras/c76acae89d43a17e3bdddb469a684552.mp4?t=1771419265\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2010900/extras/3d155d05edee32911c6370678f794e6b.avif?t=1771419265\" alt=\"作者的话\" width=568 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >首先，感谢您看到这个页面，这款游戏，并愿意浏览介绍直到这里。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >其次，需要指出的是，这是一款经费有限（庶几乎无），且是由SRPG Studio制作的游戏。作者当然知道它仅仅是无数独立游戏中的一员，既不突出，亦不伟大，更未必有什么「教化」的功效，若姑且找出一二差异，大抵是作者尚可拍拍胸脯，而后称其为「本心之作」；然而可以保证的是，这款游戏至少和SS原生的类火纹系统有着不小的差别。但其画面未能脱离SS之窠臼（亦即「经费有限」之后果），这一点亦是需要预先警醒于您的。若您对画面的不足之处可以包容的话，就请体验一下这款游戏罢！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然后，关于人民币定价为何是￥9.69这么个有零有整的数字：10和9.99都太俗，所以砍了三毛钱；此外，这个价格也代表着「火水未济」——即目前抢先体验的状态。（毕竟咱们也不好意思定￥6767.67不是？）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此外，DRM-Free！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >最后，显然Steam没有考虑过QQ群这种反馈方式，那么这里是反馈用的QQ群号：566209337。</p>",
